### Get Teacher Dashboard stats (Requires Teacher or Admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Teacher's own lessons (Requires Teacher or Admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Teacher's own groups (Requires Teacher or Admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/my-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
